HEADWORD: Alhambresque
<hw>Al`ham*bresque"</hw>
<pr>(?; 277)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <def>Made or decorated after
the fanciful style of the ornamentation in the Alhambra, which affords
an unusually fine exhibition of Saracenic or Arabesque
architecture.</def>⟦br⟧
